{"tid":381061,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"隧道口前cut線問題","createTime":"2017-08-30T15:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T09:34:05.000Z","uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"745adfeeb0cf6bd0e53f41176998993578440a35","tid":381061,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"小弟仲新，今日經將隧時候入左自動收費位，個心一亂就cut左右邊，果到係過左雙白之後既影線黎。後邊離遠一架車，右邊都冇車既。<br />\n<br />\n隧道公司會唔會票控?幾時會收信?唔該晒"},{"pid":"2d9c36fb37e376fa44bf4912c025087f19def40a","tid":381061,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:46:20.000Z","msg":"好快有人上門搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43aa840ad2493ab997016b70fc0203e21cff285a","tid":381061,"uid":4866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:52:03.000Z","msg":"你大鑊喇！"},{"pid":"c37a8cac2d8e52384e757df12dfda1b5136d26a2","tid":381061,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb67599699e4239351b3c7a85b50cddfac33bb9","tid":381061,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:02:47.000Z","msg":"去警署自首？唔係通緝左之後出唔到境"},{"pid":"ca6c743c4ed69439a4a9cf908384293e25573898","tid":381061,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"人地唔1823就無事"},{"pid":"960853d133aae1c2b5fa84a0ba94c4ecf2ca1a86","tid":381061,"uid":94218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:18:08.000Z","msg":"會好大鑊，下次唔好啦！<br />\n其實Autotoll個更亭有人架<br />\n落車大力啲敲窗就得架啦<br />\n利申 試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a02a2f606eec9f61d5667c2b2c57d4c56acf678","tid":381061,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:26:04.000Z","msg":"難分真與假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fde9aa71f53bf67d9a41a74a1e0fff6bc9cdf53","tid":381061,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:34:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會好大鑊，下次唔好啦！<br />\n其實Autotoll個更亭有人架<br />\n落車大力啲敲窗就得架啦<br />\n利申 試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無人都唔駛驚，有三個方法。<br />\n<br />\n1. 如果有辦工大樓就駛埋去問人<br />\n2. 係出口附近靠邊停就有工作人員問你，叫佢代你交就得（最好講到幾時幾分同用左邊條線）<br />\n3. 盡快打返去/電郵自首，講低咩時間咩線咩車牌行錯 Auto Toll ，佢會教你點做（可能寄支票找數/過數）。"}]}